extendedInfo.description: This is a mobile app designed for clients and potential clients of Daniel E. Morris Law Firm, PLLC.  This app allows you to call, e-mail and see us on your mobile phone.  We also help you at your accident.  Just pull out your phone and take pictures of the car accident, slip and fall, or event that caused you injury. You can even e-mail us a video of you and your accident.  Get with an attorney from Daniel E. Morris Law Firm, PLLC and get every dime you deserve!
